{"thag16.5:0.1":"Theragatha 16.5 ","thag16.5:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thag16.5:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag16.5:0.4":"Malukyaputtattheragatha ","thag16.5:1.1":"“Rupam disva sati muttha, ","thag16.5:1.2":"Piyam nimittam manasi karoto; ","thag16.5:1.3":"Sarattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:1.4":"Tanca ajjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:2.1":"Tassa vaddhanti vedana, ","thag16.5:2.2":"aneka rupasambhava; ","thag16.5:2.3":"Abhijjha ca vihesa ca, ","thag16.5:2.4":"cittamassupahannati; ","thag16.5:2.5":"Evamacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:2.6":"ara nibbana vuccati. ","thag16.5:3.1":"Saddam sutva sati muttha, ","thag16.5:3.2":"Piyam nimittam manasi karoto; ","thag16.5:3.3":"Sarattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:3.4":"Tanca ajjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:4.1":"Tassa vaddhanti vedana, ","thag16.5:4.2":"aneka saddasambhava; ","thag16.5:4.3":"Abhijjha ca vihesa ca, ","thag16.5:4.4":"cittamassupahannati; ","thag16.5:4.5":"Evamacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:4.6":"ara nibbana vuccati. ","thag16.5:5.1":"Gandham ghatva sati muttha, ","thag16.5:5.2":"Piyam nimittam manasi karoto; ","thag16.5:5.3":"Sarattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:5.4":"Tanca ajjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:6.1":"Tassa vaddhanti vedana, ","thag16.5:6.2":"aneka gandhasambhava; ","thag16.5:6.3":"Abhijjha ca vihesa ca, ","thag16.5:6.4":"cittamassupahannati; ","thag16.5:6.5":"Evamacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:6.6":"ara nibbana vuccati. ","thag16.5:7.1":"Rasam bhotva sati muttha, ","thag16.5:7.2":"Piyam nimittam manasi karoto; ","thag16.5:7.3":"Sarattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:7.4":"Tanca ajjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:8.1":"Tassa vaddhanti vedana, ","thag16.5:8.2":"aneka rasasambhava; ","thag16.5:8.3":"Abhijjha ca vihesa ca, ","thag16.5:8.4":"cittamassupahannati; ","thag16.5:8.5":"Evamacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:8.6":"ara nibbana vuccati. ","thag16.5:9.1":"Phassam phussa sati muttha, ","thag16.5:9.2":"Piyam nimittam manasi karoto; ","thag16.5:9.3":"Sarattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:9.4":"Tanca ajjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:10.1":"Tassa vaddhanti vedana, ","thag16.5:10.2":"aneka phassasambhava; ","thag16.5:10.3":"Abhijjha ca vihesa ca, ","thag16.5:10.4":"cittamassupahannati; ","thag16.5:10.5":"Evamacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:10.6":"ara nibbana vuccati. ","thag16.5:11.1":"Dhammam natva sati muttha, ","thag16.5:11.2":"Piyam nimittam manasi karoto; ","thag16.5:11.3":"Sarattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:11.4":"Tanca ajjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:12.1":"Tassa vaddhanti vedana, ","thag16.5:12.2":"aneka dhammasambhava; ","thag16.5:12.3":"Abhijjha ca vihesa ca, ","thag16.5:12.4":"cittamassupahannati; ","thag16.5:12.5":"Evamacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:12.6":"ara nibbana vuccati. ","thag16.5:13.1":"Na so rajjati rupesu, ","thag16.5:13.2":"rupam disva patissato; ","thag16.5:13.3":"Virattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:13.4":"tanca najjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:14.1":"Yathassa passato rupam, ","thag16.5:14.2":"sevato capi vedanam; ","thag16.5:14.3":"Khiyati nopaciyati, ","thag16.5:14.4":"evam so carati sato; ","thag16.5:14.5":"Evam apacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:14.6":"santike nibbana vuccati. ","thag16.5:15.1":"Na so rajjati saddesu, ","thag16.5:15.2":"saddam sutva patissato; ","thag16.5:15.3":"Virattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:15.4":"tanca najjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:16.1":"Yathassa sunato saddam, ","thag16.5:16.2":"sevato capi vedanam; ","thag16.5:16.3":"Khiyati nopaciyati, ","thag16.5:16.4":"evam so carati sato; ","thag16.5:16.5":"Evam apacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:16.6":"santike nibbana vuccati. ","thag16.5:17.1":"Na so rajjati gandhesu, ","thag16.5:17.2":"gandham ghatva patissato; ","thag16.5:17.3":"Virattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:17.4":"tanca najjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:18.1":"Yathassa ghayato gandham, ","thag16.5:18.2":"sevato capi vedanam; ","thag16.5:18.3":"Khiyati nopaciyati, ","thag16.5:18.4":"evam so carati sato; ","thag16.5:18.5":"Evam apacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:18.6":"santike nibbana vuccati. ","thag16.5:19.1":"Na so rajjati rasesu, ","thag16.5:19.2":"rasam bhotva patissato; ","thag16.5:19.3":"Virattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:19.4":"tanca najjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:20.1":"Yathassa sayarato rasam, ","thag16.5:20.2":"sevato capi vedanam; ","thag16.5:20.3":"Khiyati nopaciyati, ","thag16.5:20.4":"evam so carati sato; ","thag16.5:20.5":"Evam apacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:20.6":"santike nibbana vuccati. ","thag16.5:21.1":"Na so rajjati phassesu, ","thag16.5:21.2":"phassam phussa patissato; ","thag16.5:21.3":"Virattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:21.4":"tanca najjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:22.1":"Yathassa phusato phassam, ","thag16.5:22.2":"sevato capi vedanam; ","thag16.5:22.3":"Khiyati nopaciyati, ","thag16.5:22.4":"evam so carati sato; ","thag16.5:22.5":"Evam apacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:22.6":"santike nibbana vuccati. ","thag16.5:23.1":"Na so rajjati dhammesu, ","thag16.5:23.2":"dhammam natva patissato; ","thag16.5:23.3":"Virattacitto vedeti, ","thag16.5:23.4":"tanca najjhosa titthati. ","thag16.5:24.1":"Yathassa vijanato dhammam, ","thag16.5:24.2":"sevato capi vedanam; ","thag16.5:24.3":"Khiyati nopaciyati, ","thag16.5:24.4":"evam so carati sato; ","thag16.5:24.5":"Evam apacinato dukkham, ","thag16.5:24.6":"santike nibbana vuccati”. ","thag16.5:24.7":"… Malukyaputto thero …. "}